aces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港警民比例是 世界第五<br />\n<br />\n再加上香港無軍隊, 所以香港警察要做埋軍人果份<br />\n<br />\n外國有軍隊, 可以隨時支援警察行動<br />\n<br />\n例如, 美國發生暴動, 可以出國民警衛軍幫警察鎮壓<br />\n法國發生恐襲, 可以出憲兵/陸軍 幫警察搜捕恐怖份子<br />\n<br />\n香港警察 就自己做哂<br />\n駐港解放軍就只係花瓶, 唔可以亂用"},{"pid":"ab27676787d358373d29cc65da023f8c0d3c21c0","tid":130032,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T12:46:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警察多部門又有特警，平均訓練一個警察，淨係學堂一個人平均50萬，仲未計佢之後再上堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一路都拎最多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣真<br />\n本身有飛虎隊<br />\n又加多隊 反恐特勤"},{"pid":"8ae13a9f896376399bf6e9d7fa6d5bacfc0cbb8a","tid":130032,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T12:49:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>警察多部門又有特警，平均訓練一個警察，淨係學堂一個人平均50萬，仲未計佢之後再上堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一路都拎最多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣真<br />\n本身有飛虎隊<br />\n又加多隊 反恐特勤</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老解班少爺兵唔撚洗要錢咩？<br />\n得閒交換吓武器<br />\n用香港名義買，再俾返大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c66606f868cd8543d8e95a5ffb4c27d8e8d8b9a","tid":130032,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T12:50:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0938d8d7fc4c6e81839d4c651b40f83f7fcb1997","tid":130032,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T12:52:01.000Z","ms